CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1780488669
OL,3,CDevon and Cornwall Police 'inadequate'
OL,4,Cat safeguarding vulnerable people
OL,6,FDevon and Cornwall Police has been
OL,7,Frated inadequate at safeguarding
OL,8,Fvulnerable people and investigating
OL,9,Fcrime.
OL,11,FIn the latest PEEL (Police
OL,12,FEffectiveness, Efficiency and
OL,13,FLegitimacy) inspection carried out in
OL,14,FJanuary, His Majesty's Inspectorate
OL,15,Fsaid the force had improved how it
OL,16,Fresponds to emergency calls and how it
OL,17,Fhandles domestic abuse cases.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1780488669
OL,3,CDevon and Cornwall Police 'inadequate'
OL,4,Cat safeguarding vulnerable people
OL,6,FHowever, it found that the force
OL,7,Fdoesn't have arrangements in place to
OL,8,Fmake sure that it can always identify
OL,9,Fpeople who need to be safeguarded.
OL,11,FIt said it also "too often" found
OL,12,Fexamples of the force not having
OL,13,Fproperly dealt with domestic abuse
OL,14,Frisk assessments.
OL,16,FThe latest grading, marked over eight
OL,17,Fareas of policing, found the force was
OL,18,F"adequate" in two areas, "requires
OL,19,Fimprovement" in four areas and
OL,20,F"inadequate" in two areas.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1780488669
OL,3,CDevon and Cornwall Police 'inadequate'
OL,4,Cat safeguarding vulnerable people
OL,6,FThe force is, however, moving firmly
OL,7,Faway from the period in which it was
OL,8,Fin enhanced monitoring.
OL,10,FDevon and Cornwall Police says it's
OL,11,Fworking closely with HMICFRS, the PCC
OL,12,Fand senior leaders to accelerate
OL,13,Fprogress. It also says it has
OL,14,Fsubmitted comprehensive improvement
OL,15,Fplans.
OL,17,FInspectors will return later this year
OL,18,Fto reinspect the areas of concern and
OL,19,Freview progress.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1780488669
OL,3,CDevon and Cornwall Police 'inadequate'
OL,4,Cat safeguarding vulnerable people
OL,6,FChief constable has 'provided
OL,7,Fstability'
OL,9,FInspectors said Chief constable James
OL,10,FVaughan had contributed positively to
OL,11,Fthe overall direction of the force and
OL,12,Fprovided stability.
OL,14,FThey also said the force has improved
OL,15,Fhow quickly it answers emergency
OL,16,Fcalls, and say it has good financial
OL,17,Fmanagement.
OL,19,FThe force continues to prevent and
OL,20,Fdeter crime and antisocial behaviour
OL,21,Fwell.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1780488669
OL,3,CDevon and Cornwall Police 'inadequate'
OL,4,Cat safeguarding vulnerable people
OL,6,FHis Majesty's Inspector of
OL,7,FConstabulary Kathryn Stone OBE said:
OL,8,F"The force's ability to carry out
OL,9,Fprompt and effective criminal
OL,10,Finvestigations on behalf of victims is
OL,11,Fstill a cause of concern.
OL,13,F"It is disappointing that the force
OL,14,Fstill hasn't made enough progress on a
OL,15,Fprevious area for improvement about
OL,16,Fhow it manages medium-risk domestic
OL,17,Fabuse cases. This is a concern the
OL,18,Fforce needs to address quickly.
OL,26,@pD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1780488669
OL,3,CDevon and Cornwall Police 'inadequate'
OL,4,Cat safeguarding vulnerable people
OL,6,F"Devon and Cornwall Police is making
OL,7,Fprogress, particularly in its
OL,8,Ffinancial management, control room and
OL,9,Fprevention work.
OL,11,F"Continued focus on developing the
OL,12,Fworkforce, improving investigation
OL,13,Fstandards and safeguarding vulnerable
OL,14,Fpeople will be essential for sustained
OL,15,Fimprovement.
OL,17,F"I expect to see more progress in the
OL,18,Fareas we have set out, and I will
OL,19,Fcontinue to monitor performance."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1780488669
OL,3,CDevon and Cornwall Police 'inadequate'
OL,4,Cat safeguarding vulnerable people
OL,6,F'I recognise we are still letting some
OL,7,Fvictims down' - chief constable
OL,9,FChief constable James Vaughan said:
OL,10,F"Keeping people safe from harm and
OL,11,Fproviding the best quality service to
OL,12,Fthe public remain at the heart of
OL,13,Feverything we do.
OL,15,F"HMICFRS play an important role in
OL,16,Fholding police forces to account and
OL,17,Fprovide independent scrutiny on behalf
OL,18,Fof the public. I welcome the findings
OL,19,Ffrom the latest report.
OL,26,@rD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1780488669
OL,3,CDevon and Cornwall Police 'inadequate'
OL,4,Cat safeguarding vulnerable people
OL,6,F"Whilst we have delivered sustained
OL,7,Fimprovements since 2022 and the Force
OL,8,Fhas now been fully removed from
OL,9,Fenhanced monitoring, there remains
OL,10,Fmore to do to improve outcomes for
OL,11,Fvictims and ensure consistent
OL,12,Fsafeguarding standards.
OL,14,F"I have agreed with the Commissioner
OL,15,Fto stay in post for as long as she
OL,16,Frequires the stability provided by my
OL,17,Fleadership and I am confident that,
OL,18,Fwith the dedication of our people, we
OL,19,Fwill continue to improve our service.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1780488669
OL,3,CDevon and Cornwall Police 'inadequate'
OL,4,Cat safeguarding vulnerable people
OL,6,F"Although public trust and confidence
OL,7,Fplace us in the top ten nationally due
OL,8,Fto our firm commitment to visible
OL,9,Fneighbourhood policing, we must go
OL,10,Ffurther and do better.
OL,12,F"Many of our domestic abuse cases do
OL,13,Flead to positive outcomes, but I
OL,14,Frecognise we are still letting some
OL,15,Fvictims down.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1780488669
OL,3,CDevon and Cornwall Police 'inadequate'
OL,4,Cat safeguarding vulnerable people
OL,6,F"Getting the right outcomes for
OL,7,Fvictims is something officers and
OL,8,Fstaff care deeply about. We are
OL,9,Fplanning to move our victim care unit
OL,10,Fto Police Headquarters, helping ensure
OL,11,Fvictims remain at the centre of our
OL,12,Fwork every day.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1780488669
OL,3,CDevon and Cornwall Police 'inadequate'
OL,4,Cat safeguarding vulnerable people
OL,6,F"Officer numbers are at a record high,
OL,7,Fsupported by initiatives such as
OL,8,FOperation Resolve and a rank review
OL,9,Freturning 196 officers to the patrol
OL,10,Ffamily. These numbers include many
OL,11,Fexperienced transferees who have the
OL,12,Fskills to support complex
OL,13,Finvestigations and our new student
OL,14,Fofficers."
OL,16,FThe force said it will continue to
OL,17,Fwork closely with HMICFRS and the PCC
OL,18,Fto demonstrate sustained progress with
OL,19,Fa clear focus on delivering
OL,20,Fimprovements ahead of the next
OL,21,Finspection.uafh`
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@JO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/11
